{"tid":1322094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[排華] 加拿大華裔病毒學家邱香果及其丈夫，以及一批來自中國的學生被警方帶離國家實驗室","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T19:07:36.000Z","uid":224066,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d2aa71a92363e7ea35f4c42789d90bf50d98e296","tid":1322094,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:28:53.000Z","msg":"加拿大華裔病毒學家邱香果及其丈夫，以及一批來自中國的學生，本月五日被情報部門從加拿大國家微生物實驗室帶走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4235/4235091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4235%2F4235091.jpg&h=b464aa50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加拿大警方表示，是應公共衛生部門要求採取行動，邱香果夫婦可能涉及「政策違規」，但沒有交代詳情，相信事件對公共安全不構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n邱香果1996年到加拿大從事科研。她任職的加拿大國家微生物實驗室，是北美地區級別最高的實驗室之一，保存了包括伊波拉在內的致命病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468544-20190715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468544-20190715.htm&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=a88e99b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468544-20190715.htm&h=bb0d3b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468544-20190715.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4b8ae42fe502f25404a620c888bae949043c0cf2","tid":1322094,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:29:59.000Z","msg":"病毒學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0216fcc3ba8f42fb7fd1eb05012b597322bba3d3","tid":1322094,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a13b6130b2ab9256e9c6e785ed32c49b5f0ed1b","tid":1322094,"uid":209248,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i